          "id": "overwatch-2-is-bringing-loot-boxes-back-two-years-after-they",
          "title": "**Overwatch 2** is bringing loot boxes back, two years after they were removed from the series",
          "body": null,
          "url": "https://www.eurogamer.net/overwatch-2-is-bringing-loot-boxes-back-two-years-after-they-were-removed-from-the-series",
          "source": {
            "name": "Eurogamer",
            "domain": "eurogamer.net"
          },
          "metadata": {
            "story_type": "confirmed",
            "importance": "normal"
          },
          "bullets": [
            "The loot boxes will be available from weekly and event rewards. Players will be able to earn \"1 Legendary Loot box in the Free Battle Pass, and an additional 2 Legendary Loot boxes in the Premium Battle Pass\". The boxes themselves will allow players to earn various cosmetic pieces, such as skins and emotes."
          ]
